---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const processSteps = [
  "Site visit & conversation - we listen to how you use the space and note site conditions.",
  "Concept & itemised quote - clear scope, staging options, and allowances so nothing is hidden.",
  "Scheduling & preparation - we coordinate trades, materials, and keep neighbours informed.",
  "Construction & planting - Giles is on the tools ensuring details are finished properly.",
  "Handover & maintenance - walk-through, care notes, and optional ongoing tidy-ups.",
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | TaylorMade Landscapes, Nelson"
  description="Meet Giles Taylor - trades-qualified landscaper with 40+ years crafting practical gardens throughout Nelson and Tasman."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl space-y-12 px-4 py-12">
    <section class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.2fr] lg:items-center">
      <figure
        class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl shadow-lg transition duration-500 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:rotate-1"
        data-aos="zoom-in"
        data-aos-duration="600"
        data-aos-easing="ease-out"
      >
        <picture>
          <source srcset="/images/garden3.webp" type="image/webp" />
          <img
            src="/images/garden3.jpg"
            alt="Raised timber deck with layered native planting around a Nelson home"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </picture>
      </figure>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p
          class="badge badge-outline"
          data-aos="fade"
          data-aos-duration="450"
          data-aos-delay="50"
        >
          Meet Giles Taylor
        </p>
        <h1
          class="text-4xl font-bold"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-duration="600"
          data-aos-delay="100"
          data-aos-easing="ease-out"
        >
          40+ years shaping gardens around Nelson
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-base-content/80"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-duration="600"
          data-aos-delay="200"
          data-aos-easing="ease-out"
        >
          Giles started landscaping in the early 1980s and has worked on
          everything from compact town courtyards to sprawling coastal sections.
          His trade background means drainage, structural timber, and paving are
          completed with the same care as planting.
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-base-content/80"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-duration="600"
          data-aos-delay="300"
          data-aos-easing="ease-out"
        >
          Clients appreciate his straight talk, tidy sites, and the fact that
          he's on the tools every day-not managing from afar. When the job
          wraps, the only things left behind are clean edges and happy
          neighbours.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2
        class="text-3xl font-semibold"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="600"
        data-aos-easing="ease-out"
      >
        How we work
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-base-content/80"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="600"
        data-aos-delay="120"
        data-aos-easing="ease-out"
      >
        A clear, steady process keeps projects on track and stress-free.
        Communication is honest, pricing is transparent, and you'll always know
        who is on site.
      </p>
      <ul
        class="steps steps-vertical lg:steps-horizontal overflow-visible list-none"
      >
        {
          processSteps.map((step, index) => (
            <li
              class="step step-primary p-1"
              aria-label={step}
              data-aos="fade"
              data-aos-duration="450"
              data-aos-delay={(index * 70).toString()}
            >
              {step}
            </li>
          ))
        }
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section
      class="rounded-3xl bg-primary px-6 py-10 text-primary-content"
      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-duration="600"
      data-aos-easing="ease-out"
    >
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Let's walk your site together</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-primary-content/90">
        Whether it's a new build or a gentle refresh, a short visit is the best
        way to gauge what's possible. Bring plans, photos, or just a wishlist.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/contact"> Book a visit </a>
        <a
          class="btn btn-accent btn-outline"
          href="mailto:hello@taylormadelandscapes.nz"
        >
          Email Giles
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
